{"tid":1985374,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打試過下面流足幾星期啡色野","createTime":"2020-04-23T06:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T11:43:51.000Z","uid":61288,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d529e4377c291d301fe5b83b259af07c3404b6f3","tid":1985374,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"我經期一向唔準同亂，最近五年會間中流啡，不過最近呢兩年唔知係咪工作壓力大，一開始流一兩個星期會自動停<br />\n到最近呢兩年每半年就會有一次流足幾個星期都未完，<br />\n<br />\n2018年同2019年尾都因為黎得太長，個陣照過超聲波，冇任何異樣，醫生話係內分泌失調，食左黃體銅就冇事，之後黎正常m，最近呢個月又黎啡，睇左次中醫，食左幾次藥 係少左好多，但開始黎d帶少少淺啡既白帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊睇西醫好唔好 但我唔想又食黃體銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定睇多次中醫好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉d m咁樣 將來點生仔 好驚自己不育 因為好想同依家個男有將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打有類似經驗 真係覺得好煩同驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b378a520838630ddc4875dd1def69575a4c875cc","tid":1985374,"uid":178187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"飲多啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979b4a86064383805ae029c3b7d902a27ae3b369","tid":1985374,"uid":55321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"有冇check過有多囊卵巢綜合征之類？以往月經週期大概係點？大概咩時候流咖啡色野？"},{"pid":"867e649ee5eff2d168d3d0ac0d4fa819656efbd5","tid"